1.0.0.name: wordpress/blunt-ga
1.0.0.description:
This plugin installs Google Analytics (GA). It can be uset to set up event tracking of document, file, email, click to call and outbound links. Form submission event tracking can be set up. Event tracking can be added to all conversion pages. Cross Site tracking and linking can also be set up.

See the "Other Notes" Section for details on use.
